data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Assumable FHA loan at 2.6%. Welcome to your dream home! This stunning three-bedroom, office, 2 1/2 bath custom-built residence (with its owner designed floor-plan) is a true gem, boasting modern amenities and thoughtful design on a sprawling 1-acre lot. All bedrooms and even the master bath offer an abundance of storage above the closet space. Constructed in 2013, this immaculate home has been meticulously maintained and thoughtfully upgraded to offer the epitome of comfort and luxury.New carpet was installed in all the bedrooms in September 2023, and the home was freshly painted in August of 2023. With 10-foot ceilings and an open floor plan, the spacious living areas provide a sense of grandeur and freedom.The heart of this home is undoubtedly the custom chef's kitchen. Every detail has been carefully considered, from custom cabinets to upgraded kitchen appliances installed in 2019 and wood plank tile flooring. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or just enjoy a well-appointed kitchen, this space will delight your inner chef.Natural light floods the living areas through the upgraded windows that were replaced in 2019, creating a bright and cheerful ambiance. The 2018 replaced roof ensures peace of mind for years to come. Safety and security are paramount, and this home is equipped with a camera security system, providing you with peace of mind whether you're at home or away.Outside, the property offers practical and luxurious amenities. A screened in back porch with access to cable hook up allows you to enjoy the sunset and county life bug free. A French drain system ensures proper drainage, keeping your yard pristine even during heavy rains. A sprinkler system using well water allows you to keep your lawn lucious and green without the added expense of a water bill. For outdoor enthusiasts, a full RV hook-up with 50-amp service is a valuable addition. Additionally, the generator hook-up with a master lockout on the main panel ensures that you'll never be without power during unexpected outages. Furthermore, the property has a well-maintained shed to store all your outdoor tools, and a chicken coop equipped with your very own chickens to provide you with an endless supply of eggs.
